      "date": "2014-01-14 07:45:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nActually, I'd prefer that we continue to run lnet-selftest only as part of review-ldiskfs rather than review-dne.  The review-ldiskfs runs finish in only 3h, while review-dne takes 14-16h sometimes.  It doesn't make sense to have review-dne run longer, when lnet-selftest is testing exactly the same thing in both cases.",
